'''Vinta Corporation''' was a successful business located on the planet [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]]. They specialized in the production of ales with their most popular drink being the [[Vinta Harvest Ale]]. The company was successful enough to sponsor the [[Vinta Harvest Classic/Legends|Vinta Harvest Classic]] on Malastare, a popular [[Podracing/Legends|podrace]] that followed the [[Boonta Eve Classic/Legends|Boonta Eve Classic]].

